VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT openFile(?:Output|Input)\s*\([^,]*,\s*M(?:ODE_)?WORLD_(?:WRITEABLE|READABLE)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:EncryptedFile|openFileOutput.*MODE_PRIVATE|test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure file operations using deprecated world-readable or world-writable modes.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure File Operations.
